  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    Exporter
    The Exporter class holds a method that handles placing x and y data into a csv file.
    Function
    The Function class holds a method that calculates the answer to a mathematical function using x and y values and a method that saves the x and y values.
    FunctionCSVTester
    The FunctionCSVTester is the tester class for the Exporter, Function, Importer, Salter, and Smoother classes.
    Importer
    The Importer class contains methods to import a file and extract the contents of it.
    Salter
    The Salter class holds the method responsible for salting data that it is given, specifically the y values to a computed function.
    Smoother
    The Smoother class is responsible for taking salted data and making it more understandable.
